          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value based on data from the United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (http://data.un.org/Data.aspx?q=natural+gas&amp;d=ComTrade&amp;f=_l1Code%3a28%3bcmdCode%3a271111; accessed 12 October 2023). UN comtrade category: 271111 Natural gas, liquified. An average for 2019-2021 was used and adjusted for inflation to the year 2005. The average price of imports and exports into the five main markets (EU, US, JP, IN and CN) was determined. Density of natural gas of 0.735 kg/m³ for unit conversion was used.</comment>
        </property>
